sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Router(VllmPDRouter)
    participant SD as ServiceDiscovery(ZMQ)
    participant P as PrefillServer(kv_producer)
    participant KC as KVConnector
    participant D as DecodeServer(kv_consumer)

    rect rgb(230,245,255)
    Note over R,D: 初始化阶段
    R->>SD: 启动 ZMQ service discovery listener
    P->>SD: 注册 prefill 实例(HTTP+ZMQ地址)
    D->>SD: 注册 decode 实例(HTTP+ZMQ地址)
    opt Mooncake Connector
        R->>P: GET /query(bootstrap server)
        P-->>R: dp_rank - engine_id mapping
        Note over R: 缓存 MooncakePrefillInfo
    end
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,230)
    Note over C,D: Stage 1 - Prefill
    C->>R: POST /v1/chat/completions

    Note over R: 1. 选择 Prefill/Decode 实例
    R->>SD: get_prefill_instances()
    SD-->>R: prefill实例列表
    R->>SD: get_decode_instances()
    SD-->>R: decode实例列表
    Note over R: 通过policy选择实例(prefill_policy + decode_policy)
    Note over R: 2. 生成request_id = prefill_addr + decode_addr + uuid
    Note over R: 3. prepare_prefill_request(): max_tokens=1, stream=false

    opt Mooncake
        Note over R: kv_transfer_params = do_remote_decode:true, transfer_id:xfer-uuid
    end
    opt NIXL
        Note over R: kv_transfer_params = do_remote_decode:true, remote_engine_id:null
    end

    R->>P: POST /v1/chat/completions(max_tokens=1, kv_transfer_params, X-Request-Id)

    Note over P: EngineCore处理
    P->>P: Scheduler.get_num_new_matched_tokens()
    P->>P: CacheManager分配KV blocks
    P->>P: build_connector_meta()
    Note over P: Worker执行模型前向传播
    P->>P: start_load_kv()(异步加载远程KV)
    P->>KC: save_kv_layer(逐层保存KV到传输引擎)
    P->>KC: wait_for_save()
    Note over P: Prefill完成,生成1个token
    P->>P: request_finished()-返回kv_transfer_params
    P-->>R: Response: kv_transfer_params含remote_engine_id,remote_block_ids,remote_host,remote_port
    Note over R: 提取kv_transfer_params,释放prefill负载
    end

    rect rgb(230,255,230)
    Note over KC: KV Cache已通过RDMA/NCCL从Prefill传到Decode
    Note over C,D: Stage 2 - Decode

    Note over R: 4. 构建Decode请求
    opt Mooncake
        Note over R: kv_transfer_params = do_remote_prefill:true, transfer_id, remote_bootstrap_addr, remote_engine_id
    end
    opt NIXL
        Note over R: 直接使用prefill响应中的kv_transfer_params
    end

    R->>D: POST /v1/chat/completions(原始max_tokens, kv_transfer_params, stream=原始值)

    Note over D: EngineCore处理
    D->>D: Scheduler.get_num_new_matched_tokens()(发现远程KV可加载)
    D->>D: CacheManager分配KV blocks
    D->>KC: start_load_kv()(从远程加载KV Cache)
    loop 逐层加载+Attention
        D->>KC: wait_for_layer_load(layer_i)
        D->>D: 执行Attention(使用已加载KV)
    end
    Note over D: KV加载完成,跳过prefill,开始decode
    loop 逐token生成
        D-->>R: Stream chunk
        R-->>C: SSE data
    end
    D-->>R: data DONE
    R-->>C: data DONE
    end

    rect rgb(245,240,255)
    Note over C,R: 后处理
    opt 请求了logprobs且非流式
        R->>R: merge_logprobs(prefill_response, decode_response)
    end
    R->>R: 释放decode负载,记录PD metrics
    end
